high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the coffee maker left of the sink
Pick up the mug from the coffee maker
Turn right and walk around to the fridge
Put the mug into the fridge then take it out
Turn left and walk back around to the coffee maker
Put the mug in the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled mug in the coffee maker

high_descs: Turn around to your right. Walk around the counter to the right and stop at the coffee marker on the right.
Pick up the mug from the coffee maker.
Take the mug and turn right. Walk forward then turn right again. Face the refrigerator on your left.
Put the mug inside of the refrigerator then close it. Wait a moment then take the mug out of the refrigerator.
Turn around to the left, walk forward to the coffee machine that is on your right.
Place cup on to the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug on a coffee maker.

high_descs: Walk around the island and go to the coffee maker.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Put the mug in the fridge for a few moments and take it out again.
Go back to the coffee maker.
Put the mug in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug in the coffee maker.
